      • testParseDay

        public void testParseDay()
                  throws java.text.ParseException
        Problem for date parsing.

        This test works only correct if the short pattern of the date format is "dd/MM/yyyy". If not, this test will result in a false negative.

        Throws:
        java.text.ParseException - on parsing errors.
